description: A cartoon image of a bright yellow rubber duck. The duck has a thick black outline and wears large black sunglasses. Yellow twinkling stars are positioned around the duck. The duck has an orange bill and a blue-tinted shadow beneath it. Over the duration of the video, the duck pushes the sunglasses up, revealing eyes, after which the duck winks. A white glare appears briefly on the lens of the sunglasses. A thin, blue oval appears under the duck briefly, suggesting it is sitting on water.
